Researchprofile:

Iambothatheoreticallinguistandafieldworkerinatraditionalsense.
&nbsp;
Asatheoreticallinguist,Idoresearchinthefieldsofformalsemanticsandinterfaceofsyntaxandsemantics.Myreseachaddressesoneofthecorequestionsofhowlanguagecanbeinterpretedinacompositionalandmeaningfulway.Specifically,IworkonthestructureandcompositionalityofnominalphrasesinChineselanguages.

&nbsp;
Ialsodofieldworktodocumentundescribed(orunderdescribed)Chinesedialectsandbuildupdatabase.Withthefirst-handdatacollectedfromthefield,ItrytouncovertheinvariantpropertiesofChineselanguagesandalsotofigureouthowthe(cross-dialectal)languagevariationscanbeexplainedinaprincipledway.&nbsp;Sofar,thelanguagesIhavebeenmainlyworkingonaretheWudialectsspokeninZhejiangProvince(浙江吴语),andtheGandialects(赣语).&nbsp;

Incooperationwithmycolleagues,IstarttoworkonminoritylanguagesinChina,suchasMiao(Hmong-Mien)andZhuang(Tai-Kadai).
